<h3>About HistoryForge</h3>
<p>Sponsored by The History Center in Tompkins County, New York, HistoryForge is a system that local historical societies can use as a virtual map library. Other features coming soon.</p>
<p>In technical terms, it is built on Ruby on Rails using the open source MapWarper project as a starting point. The idea has been to remove "extra" features such as public user signup, oauth, groups, and to update the user interface in preparation for adding additional features.</p>
