<h3>About MapWarper</h3>
<p>
  Inspired by Metacarta's Map Rectifier, this is an open source map warping / geo rectifying service,
  written in Ruby and Rails. I've customised it with the OpenStreetMap project in mind.
  It's MIT licenced, so you can play with it if you want too!.
</p>

<p>Libraries and other institutions have used it, including the <a href="http://maps.nypl.org/">New York Public Library</a>, Harvard and Stanford Universities. </p>

